        Last Updated: 05/04/2025
        Welcome to JournAI. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal data is handled in a safe, responsible, and transparent manner.
        1. Data Collection
        - Personal Data: We collect your name, email, phone number, and profile picture when you register and update your profile.
        - Usage Data: We log your interactions with the app (tasks, projects, etc.) to improve your experience.
        - Device Data: We record device type, OS version, app version, IP address, and other technical information.
        2. Legal Bases for Processing
        We process your data based on your consent, the necessity for providing our services, and our legitimate interests in improving the app.
        3. Data Usage & Sharing
        Your data is used solely for operating and improving the app. It may be shared with trusted third-party service providers under strict confidentiality agreements.
        4. Data Retention & Your Rights
        We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as necessary for legal compliance. Under GDPR, you have rights to access, rectify, and erase your data.
        5. Data Security
        We employ encryption, access controls, and other security measures to protect your personal data.
        6. Contact Us
        For privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at: journaiapp@outlook.com
